name: SNAPPER 0003/1000
description: July 1st 2021. The third snapper sets foot on Terra. The blue snapper originates from the Snowy regions of viperatus. The venom of the snappers paralyzes their victims. Once paralyzed, they will lay eggs which will eat their victim from the inside out. The victim is usually still alive and fully aware of it's surroundings untill the hatchlings eat their way through vital parts of the body.
